<div class="hero-mancer chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-egg"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "HEROMANCER.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="{{patreonUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on
          Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Build your own background from the picker: choose abilities, skills, tools, and an origin feat, with GM-set
        limits.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>GM review no longer loses your colors, equipment grants, or checkbox choices, and an out-of-range ability score
        no longer blocks approval.</li>
      <li>Click anywhere on the HP method chip to open the method select, and the expertise picker now lists your current
        skills and clears stale picks.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Changes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Reopening Tokenize reloads your saved layers for editing, GM review opens faster, and more advancements apply
        automatically at creation.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "HEROMANCER.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
